title: Information for Transaero passengers with tickets for 24 October 2015 (Aeroflot OAO)
text: ( Source : Aeroflot OAO ) The following Transaero flights on 24 October 2015 have been cancelled: UN27 St. Petersburg - Vnukovo UN28 Vnukovo - St. Petersburg UN29 St. Petersburg - Vnukovo UN30 Vnukovo - St. Petersburg UN31 St. Petersburg -
